tickets.title: Fix hero section
tickets.body: The hero section of a website is like the first impression—it should be eye-catching, informative, and inviting. Consider a clean and visually appealing design with a high-quality image or illustration that reflects the essence of your brand or the content of your website. Use contrasting colors to make important elements stand out, and incorporate a concise and compelling headline that communicates your main message. Don't forget a clear call-to-action button to guide visitors to the next step.
